</listitem>
<listitem><para><citetitle>Short beginners' manual for Linux.</citetitle> Also available in Dutch. <ulink url='http://www.stuwww.kub.nl/people/b.vannunen/linux-man.php3'><citetitle>http://www.stuwww.kub.nl/people/b.vannunen/linux-man.php3</citetitle></ulink>. </para>
