</listitem>
<listitem><para><citetitle>X11 &amp; TrueType Fonts,</citetitle> by Peter Kleiweg. <ulink url='http://www.let.rug.nl/~kleiweg/'><citetitle>http://www.let.rug.nl/~kleiweg/</citetitle></ulink>. </para>
</listitem>
</itemizedlist>
 <para>Documentation for kernel developers is on-line: <ulink url='http://kernelbook.sourceforge.net'><citetitle>http://kernelbook.sourceforge.net</citetitle></ulink>. </para>
<para>To find out about Linux memory management, including performance tuning, see Rik van Riel's Web page at <ulink url='http://humbolt.geo.uu.nl/Linux-MM/'><citetitle>http://humbolt.geo.uu.nl/Linux-MM/</citetitle></ulink>.  </para>
