<para>There is also a FAQ specifically for the Red Hat Linux distribution, at <ulink url='http://www.best.com/~aturner/RedHat-FAQ/faq_index.html'><citetitle>http://www.best.com/~aturner/RedHat-FAQ/faq_index.html</citetitle></ulink>.  </para>
